-- use existing shipper_rate_date_extended in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVBLO1660187885273_shipper_rate_date_extended
-- use existing shipper_rate_date_forecast in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVJQ11660176668387_shipper_rate_date_forecast
-- use existing shipper_rate_forecast_month_agg in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVRFA1660176668375_shipper_rate_forecast_month_agg
-- use existing shipper_rate_last_date in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVQFY1660176668371_shipper_rate_last_date
-- use existing shipments_spot_last_60_days in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV2Q31660176619427_shipments_spot_last_60_days
SELECT
    (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('month', shipper_rate_date_extended."ACTUAL_DATE" ), 'YYYY-MM')) AS "shipper_rate_date_extended.date_month",
        COALESCE(SUM(( coalesce(shipper_rate_date_forecast.forecasted_volume_accepted_sum, shipper_rate_last_date.forecasted_volume_accepted_sum)  ) ), 0) + COALESCE(CAST( ( SUM(DISTINCT (CAST(FLOOR(COALESCE( (shipments_spot_last_60_days.volume_rolling_60 ) ,0)*(1000000*1.0)) AS DECIMAL(38,0))) + (TO_NUMBER(MD5( (shipments_spot_last_60_days.date_skey ) ), 'XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX') % 1.0e27)::NUMERIC(38, 0) ) - SUM(DISTINCT (TO_NUMBER(MD5( (shipments_spot_last_60_days.date_skey ) ), 'XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX') % 1.0e27)::NUMERIC(38, 0)) )  AS DOUBLE PRECISION) / CAST((1000000*1.0) AS DOUBLE PRECISION), 0) AS "shipper_rate_date_extended.volume_forecast",
        COALESCE(SUM(( coalesce(shipper_rate_date_forecast.forecasted_revenue_sum, shipper_rate_last_date.forecasted_revenue_sum)  ) ), 0) + COALESCE(CAST( ( SUM(DISTINCT (CAST(FLOOR(COALESCE( (shipments_spot_last_60_days.revenue_rolling_60 ) ,0)*(1000000*1.0)) AS DECIMAL(38,0))) + (TO_NUMBER(MD5( (shipments_spot_last_60_days.date_skey ) ), 'XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX') % 1.0e27)::NUMERIC(38, 0) ) - SUM(DISTINCT (TO_NUMBER(MD5( (shipments_spot_last_60_days.date_skey ) ), 'XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX') % 1.0e27)::NUMERIC(38, 0)) )  AS DOUBLE PRECISION) / CAST((1000000*1.0) AS DOUBLE PRECISION), 0) AS "shipper_rate_date_extended.revenue_forecast",
        COALESCE(SUM(( coalesce(nullif(shipper_rate_date_forecast.forecasted_margin_sum,0), nullif(shipper_rate_last_date.forecasted_margin_sum,0), nullif((coalesce(shipper_rate_date_forecast.forecasted_revenue_sum, shipper_rate_last_date.forecasted_revenue_sum))*(shipper_rate_forecast_month_agg.forecasted_margin_sum/nullif(shipper_rate_forecast_month_agg.forecasted_revenue_sum,0)),0))  ) ), 0) + COALESCE(CAST( ( SUM(DISTINCT (CAST(FLOOR(COALESCE( (shipments_spot_last_60_days.margin_rolling_60 ) ,0)*(1000000*1.0)) AS DECIMAL(38,0))) + (TO_NUMBER(MD5( (shipments_spot_last_60_days.date_skey ) ), 'XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX') % 1.0e27)::NUMERIC(38, 0) ) - SUM(DISTINCT (TO_NUMBER(MD5( (shipments_spot_last_60_days.date_skey ) ), 'XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX') % 1.0e27)::NUMERIC(38, 0)) )  AS DOUBLE PRECISION) / CAST((1000000*1.0) AS DOUBLE PRECISION), 0) AS "shipper_rate_date_extended.margin_forecast"
FROM LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVBLO1660187885273_shipper_rate_date_extended AS shipper_rate_date_extended
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVJQ11660176668387_shipper_rate_date_forecast AS shipper_rate_date_forecast ON shipper_rate_date_forecast.id = (shipper_rate_date_extended."SHIPPER_RATE_ID") and shipper_rate_date_forecast.date_skey = shipper_rate_date_extended.date_skey
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVRFA1660176668375_shipper_rate_forecast_month_agg AS shipper_rate_forecast_month_agg ON (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('month', shipper_rate_forecast_month_agg.date_month), 'YYYY-MM')) = (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('month', shipper_rate_date_extended."ACTUAL_DATE" ), 'YYYY-MM'))
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVQFY1660176668371_shipper_rate_last_date AS shipper_rate_last_date ON shipper_rate_last_date.id = (shipper_rate_date_extended."SHIPPER_RATE_ID") and shipper_rate_date_extended.date_skey > shipper_rate_last_date.date_skey and shipper_rate_last_date.is_last_business_day and shipper_rate_last_date.is_latest_network_rfp
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV2Q31660176619427_shipments_spot_last_60_days AS shipments_spot_last_60_days ON shipper_rate_date_extended.date_skey = shipments_spot_last_60_days.date_skey and (shipper_rate_date_extended."SHIPPER_RATE_ID")=0
WHERE ((( shipper_rate_date_extended."ACTUAL_DATE"  ) >= ((DATEADD('month', -24, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))))) AND ( shipper_rate_date_extended."ACTUAL_DATE"  ) < ((DATEADD('month', 25, DATEADD('month', -24, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))))))))
GROUP BY
    (DATE_TRUNC('month', shipper_rate_date_extended."ACTUAL_DATE" ))
ORDER BY
    1 DESC
FETCH NEXT 500 ROWS ONLY
